---
import { site } from '../data/site';
---
<article class="campus-card"><div><span class="eyebrow">Acceso externo</span><h2>Campus Virtual</h2><p>El entorno académico continúa funcionando de manera independiente. Accedé con tus credenciales habituales.</p></div><a class="button button--light" href={site.campusUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ingresar al Campus <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span><span class="sr-only">(abre en una pestaña nueva)</span></a></article>
<style>.campus-card { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; padding: clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); background: var(--green-deep); color: var(--white); }.campus-card p { max-width: 650px; margin-top: .8rem; color: #c3d5cb; }.sr-only { position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); }@media(max-width:650px){.campus-card{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column;}}</style>
